            "custom_bullets": "<p><strong>How to Participate</strong></p><ul><li>Take a photo with your custom Tarelcraft figurine</li><li>Post it on Instagram, TikTok, or Facebook</li><li>Tag @Tarelcraft and use #MyTarelcraftFigurine</li><li>Get featured on our homepage + enter the giveaway</li></ul>"
